        f"**RuVector Sources:** {', '.join(comparison['ruvector_source_set']) or 'none'}",
        f"**RuVector Families:** {', '.join(comparison['ruvector_families']) or 'none'}",
        f"**Stage 3A Sources:** {', '.join(comparison['stage3a_source_set']) or 'none'}",
        f"**Stage 3A Families:** {', '.join(comparison['stage3a_families']) or 'none'}",
        "",
        "---",
        "",
        "## Answerability / Direct Evidence",
        "",
        f"- **Answerability intent:** `{comparison['answerability_intent']}`",
        f"- **RuVector direct evidence count:** {comparison['direct_evidence_count_ruvector']}",
        f"- **Stage 3A direct evidence count:** {comparison['direct_evidence_count_stage3a']}",
